{"tid":1982433,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"世衛讚新加坡：雖面臨挑戰但有能力處理","createTime":"2020-04-21T08:07:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T12:48:31.000Z","uid":133680,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"05bcd6d37a17a6cbdc6eb140ab2ea44bce001589","tid":1982433,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:07:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3140600\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3140600&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiZ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=673ddcf8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3140600&h=ac37a716\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3140600</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕新加坡防疫措施破功，短短1個月就從數百起武漢肺炎病例暴增到現在的8000餘人感染，但世界衛生組織（WHO）西太平洋區域主任葛西健（Takeshi Kasai）對此表示，新加坡雖然面臨病毒的挑戰，基本上還是有能力處理的。<br />\n<br />\n據《路透》報導，葛西健表示，新加坡必須要應對急劇增加的新型冠狀病毒感染，這樣的挑戰十分艱鉅，但新加坡過去擁有相關經驗，再加上其醫療系統和風險管理能力，應該還是可以處理得不錯。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡目前有8014人確診武漢肺炎，是東南亞病例最多的國家。"},{"pid":"a8ef1113dbe2dd30771c3cb71db500483ef584bc","tid":1982433,"uid":187987,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:08:36.000Z","msg":"幾時讚下香港?"},{"pid":"80512d1db6b9f174d5d83c2072d5687d629c4ea6","tid":1982433,"uid":49208,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"a8ef1113dbe2dd30771c3cb71db500483ef584bc","tid":1982433,"uid":187987,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:08:36.000Z","msg":"幾時讚下香港?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:09:25.000Z","msg":"讚得好呀，繼續讚新加坡<br />\n咪撚燈香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b84564fc006c2aa1c1f9f9b25b0831d101a550","tid":1982433,"uid":123774,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:10:34.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好讚香港<br />\n恥與世衛同行"},{"pid":"72b7a11654cf418cfd2e20cb0121cd869d188751","tid":1982433,"uid":302